---
import Layout from '@layouts/LayoutPage.astro';
const yearsExperience = new Date().getFullYear() - 2018;
---

<Layout title="About me">
  <h1 class="text-2xl text-green-orange font-bold">About me</h1>
  <p>
    Nice to meet you, I&apos;m Giovanni Callegari, software developer with {yearsExperience}+ years
    of experience. Enthusiast in web development with a passion for building digital products.{' '}
    <br />I love the entire process of development: from the concept, brainstorming sessions, all
    the way to solving real-life problems with code.
  </p>
  <ol class="relative border-l border-gray-200 border-gray-700 my-4">
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400">1999</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Born</h3>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2013-2018</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">High school diploma</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">
        Computer science diploma at I.T.T. Eugenio Barsanti in Italy
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2018-2020</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Full-stack web developer</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">
        I worked as full-stack web developer in Italian software house specialized in ERP to food
        factories.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2020 to 2022</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Backend developer</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">
        I joined a team of .NET developers in education software provider to Italian and
        Switzerland&apos;s private schools.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2020 to present</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Freelance</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">I&apos;ve worked as backend developer</p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2022 to 2023</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Mid full stack developer</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">
        I worked for 6 months as a fullstack developer in IT consultancy multinational company
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-6 ml-4">
      <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-[0.36rem] bg-neutral-500">
      </div>
      <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-neutral-400"> 2023 to present</time>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">React developer</h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-neutral-500">
        I am working as a React developer in a startup located in Milan
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>
  <h2 class="text-xl text-green-orange font-semibold">Approach</h2>
  <p>
    During coding sessions I really like to collaborate with other team workers, showing my best
    value. I believe in team working, to share ideas and then to create magic ! <br />
    <br />I consider myself a &apos;
    <a
      class="text-darkgreen dark:text-green font-bold"
      href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_principle"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer">
      first principle thinker
    </a>
    &apos;: my approach to problem-solving, not only in terms of coding, is regulated by an analysis
    destructured of problems.
    <br />
    In doing so I can focus on the smaller problems of the main one, so, I can channel my energy to solve
    the problem deeper, with more awareness of it.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-xl text-green-orange font-semibold">Also</h2>
  <p>
    Software development is also a passion of mine, indeed I like to follow new courses or build
    upon actual knowledge to master it. Besides I spend some time completing personal projects,
    thanks to other developer friends too.
    <br />
    <br />
    In addition I really love sports, especially do weights, also basketball and swimming which are my
